    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving the original factory paint which remains free of swirls, rock chips, or imperfections. The exterior has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating to ensure long-term protection and a deep, mirror-like shine. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and smoke-free; the leather bolsters show no signs of entry wear, the carpets are protected by original floor mats, and every button and switch operates with crisp, factory-new precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It comes with a binder of exhaustive service records from a certified dealership, confirming that all scheduled maintenance is up to date. The engine bay is detailed and dry, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This sale includes the full set of original keys, the owner's manual, and a clean title in hand. For the buyer who demands perfection without compromise, this is the one.",
